quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,42,"Taura kuti: “Ndiani angakudzivirirei usiku nesikati kubva kumupi ane nyasha (Allah)?” Asi vanopira makotsi kune rangaridzo (yeuchidzo) yaTenzi vavo"
  21,43,"Kana kuti vane vamwe vanamwari (vekunyepera) vanovadzivirira kubva kwatiri? Havana simba rekuzvibatsira, kana kuti vave vanodzivirirwa kubva kwatiri (kubva kumurango wedu)"
  21,44,Asi takavapa ava nemadzibaba avo kugarika kweupenyu uhwu kusvika pakuti nguva (yekurarama) yakavarebera. Havaoni here kuti nyika iri kutapudzwa (hutongi hwavo huri kutapudzwa) kubva kumiganhu yavo? Nokudaro ndivo here vachakunda (muhondo)
  21,45,"Taura (Muhammad (SAW)) kuti: “Zvirokwazvo, ini ndinokuyambirai neizvo zvandakatumirwa (Qur’aan).” Asi avo vasinganzwi (vane nharo vanongotevera zvitendero vasingazivi zvirimo) havanzwi sheedzo apo vanenge vachiyambirwa (kuti munhu anofanira kutevedzera Qur’aan ne Sunnah (Nzira) yaMuhammad (SAW)"
  21,46,"Uye kana kachidimbu kemarwadzo aTenzi vako kavawira, zvirokwazvo, vanotaura kuti: “Maiwe (Marwadzo kwatiri)! Zvirokwazo, taiva vatadzi vakuru.”"
  21,47,"Tichava tinogadzika zvikero zvinoenzanisa (zvisingabiridziri) pazuva rekutongwa, zvokuti hapana munhu achadzvanyirirwa kunyange nepadiki pose (pakaita sei). Uye kana pane chicharema zvishoma kurema kwekamhodzi kadiki, tichachiburitsa pachena. Tisu tinokwanisa kutonga"
  21,48,"Uye takava tinopa Musa naHaaroon (Aroni) chipatsanuro (chezvakanaka nezvakaipa), uye chiedza chinopenya (Torah), uye neyeuchidzo kune avo vanotya Allah"
  21,49,"Avo vanotya Tenzi vavo kunyange vasingavaoni, uye vanotya Nguva (zuva rekutongwa)"
  21,50,Uye iyi iyeuchidzo yakakomborerwa yatakadzikisa. Saka munoiramba here